{"recommendationid": "12151443", "author": {"steamid": "76561197972875431", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 23, "playtime_forever": 2396, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 2396, "last_played": 1410925068}, "language": "english", "review": "I never heard of this game until it was released, so my expectation were not driven by all of the media hype that most other people are complaining about. Also of all the time I've spent playing the game I have only had it crash on me once, and I have only experienced Uplay being down once. I know the game and Uplay have their problems but some people like to blow things out of proportion when they complain.

